  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >In this relaxing first person voyage you'll sail towards the sunset through magical waters in a very special boat. You won't have to worry about steering, logistics, missing crewmembers, capsizing or even pirates. It's a trip for you to sit back and... becalm!</h2><br><br><i><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>    Bright and dreamy watercolor aesthetics that bring to life multiple biomes.<br></li><li>    An awesome synthesizer ensemble cascading through field recorded maritime soundscapes.<br></li><li>    Every time you play it'll randomly select a journey for you.<br></li><li>    Choose between a five minute journey or endless mode.<br></li><li>    Relax.</li></ul></i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/999830/extras/1c0cac0d8838c50ce2ad421ccb048bed.webp?t=1578641309\" width=616 height=62 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/999830/extras/fe80ffff9856e57f58d4fd55c4d0e958.poster.avif?t=1578641309\" width=616 height=283 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/999830/extras/fe80ffff9856e57f58d4fd55c4d0e958.webm?t=1578641309\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/999830/extras/2af36e120c9c15430bc8aa305be52e7b.webp?t=1578641309\" width=616 height=62 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/999830/extras/fc02ad94583fc64eab8097ed6d0bf8d7.poster.avif?t=1578641309\" width=800 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/st